{"tid":1134877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix與奧巴馬夫妻合作 推新劇批特朗普","createTime":"2019-05-02T03:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T03:18:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a166f97dc93c11be4ac733241310052493b08d0e","tid":1134877,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"美國視頻串流服務商Netflix公布，與奧巴馬夫妻成立的製作公司Higher Ground Productions的初步合作計劃，其中包括改編自劉易斯(Michael Lewis)原作《第五風險》(The Fifth Risk)的劇集。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年出版的《第五風險》措詞嚴厲批評特朗普，指摘現屆政府做了不少愚蠢事情，將美國帶向極為危險的境地。<br />\n<br />\n據法新社報道，Netflix一年前宣布與奧巴馬夫婦簽訂電影和劇集製作的多年合約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2126878/Netflix推劇批特朗普+奧巴馬當製片\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2126878%2FNetflix%E6%8E%A8%E5%8A%87%E6%89%B9%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%2B%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E7%95%B6%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%87&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmd%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=809d259e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2126878/Netflix推劇批特朗普+奧巴馬當製片</a>"}]}